g.title: AWS CloudFormation Sample Template LAMP_Single_Instance_With_RDS: Create a LAMP stack using a single EC2 instance for the web server and an Amazon RDS database instance for the backend data store. This template demonstrates using the AWS CloudFormation bootstrap scripts to install the packages and files necessary to deploy the Apache web server and PHP at instance launch time. **WARNING** This template creates an Amazon EC2 instance and an Amazon RDS DB instance. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.
